Package: stCEG
Title: Fully Customisable Chain Event Graphs over Spatial Areas
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Hollie", "Calley", email = "hc629@exeter.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 'stCEG' is an R package with an integrated 'Shiny' interface that facilitates the creation of Chain Event Graphs (CEGs) over spatial areas. It allows users to fully customise both the structure and underlying model of the CEG, offering a high degree of flexibility for tailored analyses.
URL: https://github.com/holliecalley/stCEG
BugReports: https://github.com/holliecalley/stCEG/issues
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
